DOC.brief_summary: Back pain affects the majority of the population at some time. Currently there are no published and scientifically accepted objective measures to support manual medicine diagnostic and treatment techniques for back pain. The purpose of this project is to collect and evaluate objective (pressure and motion) data from standard clinical diagnostic tests.
DOC.criteria: HEalthy and no pain in cervical spine Pain of 3 or greater in cervical spine pain of less than 3 in the cervical spine region pregnant
